OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FAn advert for French oil and gas giant
OL,7,FTotalEnergies has been banned in the
OL,8,FUK for misleading consumers over the
OL,9,Ffirm's environmental impact.
OL,11,FCampaign group Adfree cities
OL,12,Fcomplained that the paid-for X post in
OL,13,FMay focused on the firm's renewable
OL,14,Fwind energy projects while failing to
OL,15,Fmention that its operations remained
OL,16,Fmostly based in fossil fuels.
