OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FTotalEnergies said it could not
OL,7,Finclude more information about its
OL,8,Fbusiness practices within the ad due
OL,9,Fto the constraints of the medium, but
OL,10,Fits website made clear that it was
OL,11,Finvolved in oil and gas.
OL,13,FHowever the Advertising Standards
OL,14,FAuthority (ASA) ruled that the advert,
OL,15,Fwhich focused on one of the
OL,16,FTotalEnergies' lower-carbon
OL,17,Finitiatives, framed it as reflective
OL,18,Fof its current business activity.
