OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FThe TotalEnergies' Sustainability and
OL,7,FClimate 2024 report stated that in
OL,8,F2023, 90% of its sales arose from
OL,9,Fpetroleum and gas products, while it
OL,10,Fwas responsible for 1.5% of global oil
OL,11,Fproduction and had allocated 68.3% of
OL,12,Fits capital expenditure towards fossil
OL,13,Ffuel energies and 31.7% to lower-
OL,14,Fcarbon activities.
OL,16,FThe ASA said it was therefore likely
OL,17,Fto mislead as it had not included
OL,18,Finformation about the proportion of
OL,19,FTotalEnergies' overall business model
OL,20,Fthat comprised lower-carbon energy
OL,21,Fproducts.
