OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FAlongside the ruling, the ASA did not
OL,7,Fuphold 76 complaints that an advert
OL,8,Ffor Shell gave a misleading impression
OL,9,Fof its environmental impact, or one
OL,10,Fcomplaint that an ad for Barclays bank
OL,11,Fwas misleading for omitting
OL,12,Fsignificant information about its
OL,13,Fcontribution to carbon dioxide and
OL,14,Fgreenhouse gas emissions.
