OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FIn the case of Shell, a TV ad featured
OL,7,Fan engineer walking past electric
OL,8,Fvehicle charging points, an offshore
OL,9,Fgas rig and a family kitchen before
OL,10,Fsuperimposed text detailed the
OL,11,Fproportion of the energy giant's
OL,12,Finvestments in fossil fuels and lower
OL,13,Fcarbon technologies.
OL,15,FThe ASA said the advert made it clear
OL,16,Fto consumers that the majority of
OL,17,FShell's investments were in oil and
OL,18,Fgas and therefore did not give a
OL,19,Fmisleading overall impression of its
OL,20,Fenvironmental impact.
