OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FThe rulings are part of the ASA's
OL,7,Fongoing Climate Change and Environment
OL,8,Fproject which aims to shine a greater
OL,9,Fregulatory spotlight on green claims
OL,10,Fused in advertising.
OL,12,FHowever Adfree Cities, which made
OL,13,Fcomplaints against both ads, said the
OL,14,FASA's refusal to ban the Shell advert
OL,15,Fwas "endorsing greenwash".
