OL,3,CTotalEnergies advert banned for
OL,4,Cmisleading over environmental impact
OL,6,FVeronica Wignall, co-director at
OL,7,FAdfree Cities, said: "Any advert that
OL,8,Fportrays Shell as prioritising the
OL,9,Fenvironment in any way is
OL,10,Fcategorically misleading while the oil
OL,11,Fmajor continues to expand its fossil
OL,12,Ffuel operations, directly undermining
OL,13,Fa clean energy transition.
OL,15,F"With this ruling the ASA is
OL,16,Fessentially endorsing greenwash,
OL,17,Fmarking a systemic and ongoing failure
OL,18,Fto protect consumers from fossil fuel
OL,19,Fmisinformation."
